# INCIDENT: Network policy misconfiguration
# DATE: 2024-02-20
# SEVERITY: CRITICAL
# AFFECTED SERVICES: api-gateway, payment-service,
#                    database-service, auth-service
# ROOT CAUSE: Kubernetes NetworkPolicy update accidentally blocked
#             ingress traffic between sre-demo and default namespaces.
#             All inter-service communication dropped after policy
#             was applied during routine maintenance window.
# RESOLUTION: Identified misconfigured NetworkPolicy using kubectl
#             describe. Rolled back NetworkPolicy to previous version.
#             All inter-service traffic restored within 3 minutes.
#             Added policy validation step to change management process.
# STATUS: RESOLVED
